events.title: 3-Day Arduino-Based Robotics Bootcamp
events.description: From Basics to Intelligent Robots Robotics teaches the practical use of circuits, control systems, sensors, and motors while building strong problem-solving and system-level thinking skills. This bootcamp is designed for EEE and tech-enthusiastic students who want to turn logic into real, working robots.

announcements.title: Reminder: All-Members General Meeting Next Week
announcements.content: Greetings members! A mandatory general meeting has been scheduled to discuss upcoming projects and the budget for the new year. Please ensure you attend. * Date: Wednesday, January 15, 2026 * Time: 7:00 PM - 8:30 PM * Location: Conference Room B (or via Zoom link: [Insert Link Here]) * Agenda Highlights: 1. Q2 Project Review 2. Annual Budget Approval 3. Volunteer sign-ups for the Spring Fair. We look forward to seeing you there!
